ing weapons. Since I can't use 'em, might as well tell ya what NOT to go after.<P>These are the obvious ones:<BR>Sarnak Liberator (Drops off Sarnak flunkie in Lake of Ill Omen)<P>Goblin Slaver's Whip (drops off goblin slaverdriver/taskmaster)<P>Goblin Knee splinter (Drops off goblin whelps in Lake of Ill Omen)<P>Goblin Skinner (Drops off the Goblin Battlemaster in Lake of Ill Omen)<P>Blade of Passage (Drops off any Sarnak. I've seen it drop from a recruit and legionnaire)<P>As for the weapons and stats..they are all PITIFUL EXCEPT for the Sarnak liberator...which is 6/41 Effect:Spirit strike. Spirit strike is a 88 point dd (Which is better than ykesha's effect)<BR>Oh well, no point in going after an item I can't HIT anything with.<P>Lanse the Frustrated<BR>Vicar of Bristlebane<P>PS-Not like anyone cares, but I just spent 50 of my training points in advancing my hand to hand combat for no reason...because it was atleast a better cause than wasting countless hours and a whole bottle of aspiriin/tylenol extra strength.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
